fr.univ_tours.li.mdjedaini.ideb.eval

Class Exploration

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.univ_tours.li.mdjedaini.ideb.eval.Exploration
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TaskResolution

    public class Exploration
extends java.lang.Object
    Task resolution objects contains all the details of what happened during a resolution of task by a SUT. It represents the session that is obtained by the task resolution process. We record the session and other things like what generated the query, the user or the SUT, and many other things to keep details on the evaluation.
